OL,3,CFuel price row rumbles on as Centrica
OL,4,Cprofits hit #1bn
OL,6,FThe parent company of British Gas
OL,7,Ftoday has announced profits of a
OL,8,Fbillion pounds.
OL,10,FAlthough the company says its half-
OL,11,Fyear earnings from energy customers
OL,12,Fare lower than last year.
OL,14,FMeanwhile, fuel poverty campaigners
OL,15,Fhave accused it of unfair profiteering.
OL,17,FOf Centrica's #1 billion overall
OL,18,Fprofits for the first half of 2024,
OL,19,Fits earnings from the British Gas
OL,20,Fdivision fell from #969m to #159m.
